HEADWORD: Knittle
<hw>Knit"tle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Knit</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A string that draws together a
purse or bag.</def> <mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark>
